		<section class="mt-16 w-full">
			<h2 class="text-2xl tracking-tight text-stone-950 sm:text-3xl">
				Executive summary
			</h2>
			<div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-base leading-8 text-stone-700 sm:text-lg">
				<p>
					We took a sidelined browser extension with 12M+ installs and brought
					it back into the spotlight. Along with a brand new visual style,
					reformed information architecture, and a revised feature set, we
					introduced an interactive Privacy Advisor guide system.
				</p>
				<p>
					Through a meticulous design and development process, our team
					delivered a fully refreshed product to praise from users and
					leadership. Avast Online Security &amp; Privacy made a strong return
					and started to play <strong class="font-bold text-stone-950"
						>an integral role as a major digital touchpoint</strong
					> for both existing and potential customers.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

